<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: bliss lobotomy -->
  <BlissLobotomy.label>至福のロボトミー</BlissLobotomy.label>
  <!-- EN: Remove part of a person's brain, placing them in a state of bliss while rendering them incapable of intellectual and skilled labor. They will also learn more slowly, and be less likely to rebel or attempt a prison break. -->
  <BlissLobotomy.description>人の脳の一部を切除し,至福状態にします.知的労働や技術を要する作業が行えなくなり,学習速度も低下しますが,反乱や脱獄を試みる可能性も低くなります.</BlissLobotomy.description>
  <!-- EN: Lobotomizing TargetA. -->
  <BlissLobotomy.jobString>TargetAをロボトミー手術中</BlissLobotomy.jobString>
  
  <!-- EN: ghoul infusion -->
  <GhoulInfusion.label>グール注入</GhoulInfusion.label>
  <!-- EN: Infuse a living person with an archotech shard to create a terrifying creature known as a ghoul. Ghouls are ferocious melee fighters and are incapable of work. They eat raw meat to survive but never sleep. Hungry ghouls are dangerous.\n\nGhouls created by this operation will be a part of your colony. -->
  <GhoulInfusion.description>生きている人間にアルコテックの破片を注入し,グールとして知られる恐ろしい生物を生み出します.グールは凶暴な近接戦闘員で,作業を行えません.生きるために生肉を食べますが,眠ることはありません.飢えたグールは危険な存在です.\n\nこの手術によって生み出されたグールは,コロニーの住民として扱えます.</GhoulInfusion.description>
  <!-- EN: Ghoulizing TargetA. -->
  <GhoulInfusion.jobString>TargetAをグール化中</GhoulInfusion.jobString>
  
  <!-- EN: surgical inspection -->
  <SurgicalInspection.label>外科調査</SurgicalInspection.label>
  <!-- EN: An invasive surgery to find any hidden abnormalities within a patient. -->
  <SurgicalInspection.description>患者の体内の隠れた異常を見つける侵襲的手術.</SurgicalInspection.description>
  <!-- EN: Surgically inspecting TargetA. -->
  <SurgicalInspection.jobString>TargetAを外科調査している</SurgicalInspection.jobString>
  
</LanguageData>